    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/cpb-hemolysis-decision-001",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The experimental hemolysis dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-22) predates the November 2025 mesh-topology revision (modelRevisionDate 2025-11-14); however, the revision team documented the change as a minor volute trailing-edge refinement with no expected impact on bulk hemolysis predictions. The team accepted this assessment without conducting formal re-validation against post-revision experimental data. Mean NIH error of 8.3% and RH = 0.87 provide sufficient margin against the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Overall credibility assessment: Accepted for the stated COU.",
